#. ID 1, Page 1, Line 1, Pos (10,5)
#. ID 1, Page 2, Line 1, Pos (10,5)
msgid ""
"『七つの色彩……絵の具玉を　集めよ\n"
"　さすれば　部屋は色づき\n"
"　そなたの　架け橋となるだろう』"
msgstr ""
"\"Collect the seven balls of paint...\n"
"Then the room will be colored,\n"
"and your bridge will be made.\""

#. ID 1, Page 1, Line 6, Pos (10,5)
msgid ""
"\n"
"「絵の具玉……？\n"
"　そんなもの　どこに　あるのかしら」"
msgstr ""
"\n"
" Balls of paint...?\n"
" I wonder where those are..."

#. ID 1, Page 3, Line 1, Pos (10,5)
msgid ""
"『七つの色彩が　集まった\n"
"　これにて　一件落着』"
msgstr ""
"\"The seven colors are assembled.\n"
"Thus settles the matter.\""

